""
"" mapping du clavier bépo->qwerty en mode normal
""

" configuration des lettres

noremap b q
noremap bà aw
noremap bu as
noremap bj ap
noremap bk ab
noremap bK aB
noremap é w
noremap p e
noremap o r
noremap è t
noremap ^ y
noremap ^n ^m
noremap v u
noremap d i
noremap l o
noremap j p
noremap z [
noremap zj [p
noremap w ]
noremap wj ]p
